43:34.500 --> 43:35.966
Smart boy!

43:37.866 --> 43:39.333
But the game's gotta end.

43:39.400 --> 43:41.333
Ah!

43:46.233 --> 43:48.900
Urgh!

43:48.966 --> 43:51.200
Ruined a perfectly good sweater.

43:53.833 --> 43:55.900
Here, take it.

43:58.666 --> 44:00.533
